<br>
So he just keeps clicking his staff and gets huge aggro on the mob, while he is doing this I send in my pet (I used 54 water for BS but any none rooting pet will work) and the pet beats on the mob. He just keeps clicking and running in circles the whole time holding the aggro from the mob and since the stick has an instant cast he never even has to slow down. Jboots help but Sow helps alot here and he doesn't get hit running from the mob though this takes some practice. Eventually the mob dies and and we just do it again. I also throw a nuke in here and there to speed things along.<br>
<br>
We then just do it again until his finger gets tired. This is nothing new but with all the post 50 group things I have been seeing thought I would post yet another way to get exp easily and safely with friends and I am kind of bored at work. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/urunemaker.showPublicProfile?language=EN>RuneMaker</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Elementalist</span><br>  Posts: 80<br> <font color=#333333>(11/15/01 5:11:17 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerthingstokill.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=320.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Hate Kiting</span><hr size=1> <br>
